dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Marinette County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Marinette County, Wisconsin in 2020, and includes the layers 'MARINETTE_HYDRO_2020_LINE', and 'MARINETTE_HYDRO_2020_POLY'. [The hydroarc shapefile represents the lakes, ponds, rivers and streams in Marinette County, Wisconsin. Data is referenced to the Marinette County Coordinate System, North American Datum 1983 with the 1991 adjustment (NAD83/91).]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
